		<tr>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Verant needs to put up a webpage that gives the backstory to the game, and answers questions like: <br>  <br> 1. Who is Firiona Vie?  What class and level, if any? <br>  <br> 2. Who is the ruler of Freeport?  What is his title?  Is he a King?  Mayor? <br>  <br> 3. Why are the Freeport Militia and the Freeport paladins/clerics at war?  (And no, &quot;Because the Militia is corrupt&quot; is not a sufficient answer.)  How and when did the Militia become corrupt? <br>  <br> 4. How did Neriak become allied with Crushbone, and why isn't it allied with any other group of orcs? <br>  <br> 5. What happened to the Combine Empire?  And why was it named the &quot;Combine&quot; Empire. <br>  <br> 6. How did Kithicor change, and why? <br>  <br> 7. What is the story behind Highpass Hold?  Who founded it and when? <br>  <br> 8. Why and why did the continent of Tunaria get renamed Antonica?  Why did the elves leave Tunaria for Faydwer? <br>  <br> 9. How and when was old Sebilis destroyed in Kunark?		

